text: The canton of Boulogne-sur-Mer-1 is an administrative division of the Pas-de- Calais department, in northern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Boulogne- sur-Mer.Décret n° 2014-233 du 24 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département du Pas-de-Calais It consists of the following communes: #Boulogne-sur-Mer (partly) #La Capelle-lès-Boulogne #Conteville-lès-Boulogne #Pernes-lès-Boulogne #Pittefaux #Wimereux #Wimille ==References== Category:Cantons of Pas-de-Calais
